---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best External SSD for Backup 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of portable SSDs. Fast backup and file transfer for creatives and professionals.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best External SSD for Backup</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · 1050MB/s</div>

      <p>External SSDs are essential for fast backups and file transfers. After testing multiple portable drives, one stands out for its blazing speed, compact size, and built-in security features — perfect for creatives and professionals on the go.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 Samsung T7 Portable SSD</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>1050MB/s read speed, 1000MB/s write</strong> — blazing fast transfers</li>
          <li><strong>USB-C and USB-A cables included</strong> — works with any device</li>
          <li><strong>Fingerprint security scanner built-in</strong> — protect sensitive data</li>
          <li><strong>Shock-resistant aluminum unibody</strong> — durable construction</li>
          <li><strong>Weighs only 2 ounces, credit card size</strong> — ultra portable</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=samsung+t7+ssd&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it wins at this price</h3>
      <p>Most portable SSDs compromise on speed or security. The Samsung T7 delivers consistent 1050MB/s read speeds with hardware encryption and optional fingerprint protection. The aluminum body is both lightweight and durable enough for daily commuting.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Creatives, professionals, and anyone who needs fast, reliable backup on the go. It's perfect for photographers, video editors, and anyone who transfers large files regularly.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>